<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h2 class="h4">
      You have
      <span class="bold number-title">3</span>
      {{#if ship}}<span class="bold">EOBs</span>{{else}}<span class="bold eob-title">Medical EOBs</span>{{/if}} for the
      <span class="bold days-title">Last 90 days</span>
    </h2>
    <p>
      {{#if ship}}
      EOB statements that were created prior to December 2013 will not be posted to this site. EOB statements posted to this site will look slightly different than EOB statements that included a check. The electronic copies do not include an image of the check.
      {{else}}
      The Medical EOB is a summary of the claims we get for your medical care in a particular month. For example, if we get claims in April, you’ll get a EOB in May. If there are no claims in May, you won’t get a EOB in June.
      {{/if}}
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
