  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p>In some instances, the “Download EOB” link may open an Explanation of Payment (PDF) if you are owed money based on your health care claims.</p>
      <p class="margin-none">
        <span class="bold">Is there a provider listed on an EOB that you do not recognize?</span>
        There are times when your doctor contracts with a facility or a lab for services. If you have any questions about your EOB,
        <a href="#" class="lowercase">contact UnitedHealthcare</a>.
